  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a condensed bubble of super dense air around you in an attempt to deflect incoming attacks. Roll 3d8. The result of the roll is the amount of damage your air Bubble can prevent before it bursts. This lasts until the beginning of your next turn. Lightning Damage deals half as much damage to your air bubble and Fire Damage deals twice as much.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and roll an additional 1d8.</p>",
